						| Are you suffering from acute or chronic neck or back pain? Are you ready to get back to enjoying all that life has to offer? Look no further. We can help you.  Call our Total Spine Specialty Clinic to schedule your appointment right away.  Most patients experience significant improvement in the first visit!
				p
					| Our Total Spine Specialty Clinic was developed by one of the most respected and sought after physical therapy spine specialists, 
					a(href='../therapists.php#atkinson') Teresa A. Atkinson, PT, MDT
